<span class="hl_keyword">lemma</span> aborted_and_resolved_exclusive:<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;all-traces<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class="hl_operator">¬</span><span class="hl_operator">(</span><span class="hl_operator">∃ </span>ct #i #j<span class="hl_operator">.</span><br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="hl_operator">(</span>AbortCert( ct ) <span class="hl_operator">@</span> #i<span class="hl_operator">)</span> <span class="hl_operator">∧</span> <span class="hl_operator">(</span>ResolveCert( ct ) <span class="hl_operator">@</span> #j<span class="hl_operator">)</span><span class="hl_operator">)</span>&quot;<br/>
<a class="internal-link edit" href="/thy/trace/1/main/edit/aborted_and_resolved_exclusive">edit lemma</a>  or  <a class="internal-link delete" href="/thy/trace/1/main/delete/aborted_and_resolved_exclusive">delete lemma</a><br/>
<span class="hl_keyword">by</span> <a class="internal-link proof-step sorry-step" href="/thy/trace/1/main/proof/aborted_and_resolved_exclusive"><span class="hl_keyword">sorry</span></a><br/>
<br/>
